{"tid":979594,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[網絡白痴求救] 有無router有兩個WiFi interface？","createTime":"2019-01-12T19:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T09:06:25.000Z","uid":43015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39aff875875c7a2dba98245665432dd55964388f","tid":979594,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T19:16:48.000Z","msg":"宜家我用緊兩部router<br />\n一部當access point用，放WiFi俾房裏面啲電腦用，做電腦之間嘅Intranet<br />\n一部就收另一個有Internet access嘅WiFi，拎嚟做上Internet嘅gateway<br />\n<br />\n宜家有一部router壞咗<br />\n趁住買新router<br />\n想睇吓有無router有兩個WiFi interface<br />\n裝吓類似DD-WRT嗰啲custom firmware<br />\n可以做到兩個WiFi interface一收一放<br />\n唔使分開兩部router咁煩<br />\n<br />\n間房無上到Internet嘅LAN線頭，但係房裏面有啲電腦無得插LAN線，所以先要搞到咁複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fdd161d6ed6e87dd61acfac9213bb08a4ef3c8","tid":979594,"uid":65408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T19:55:45.000Z","msg":"用  mesh wifi router 得唔得？"},{"pid":"cd99471e72b05e1f6918f3d8a2d05ede47bbfd33","tid":979594,"uid":91754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T20:28:48.000Z","msg":"$$$問題，你個情況，一隻router做唔到咩？"},{"pid":"b991430936cef5745bad5047445f9798edced59f","tid":979594,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd99471e72b05e1f6918f3d8a2d05ede47bbfd33","tid":979594,"uid":91754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T20:28:48.000Z","msg":"$$$問題，你個情況，一隻router做唔到咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:29:45.000Z","msg":"一隻普通router做到同時收WiFi同放WiFi咩？<br />\n我唔多熟router<br />\n剩係試過用raspberr Pi當router<br />\nWiFi interface當咗access point就無得收WiFi"},{"pid":"da80373b4dc37c45ca882b8eb2825eb4db517c96","tid":979594,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:54:10.000Z","msg":"唔該哂樓上兩位巴打<br />\n靠你哋嘅資料我Google到WiFi Repeater好似係我想要嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.dd-wrt.com/wiki/index.php/Client_Mode_Wireless\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.dd-wrt.com%2Fwiki%2Findex.php%2FClient_Mode_Wireless&d=sjxcN0XPNtZU4ybn6Crpjcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ff3ed7e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.dd-wrt.com/wiki/index.php/Client_Mode_Wireless</a><br />\n<br />\n但係應該買個專門嘅WiFi repeater定用DD-WRT改好？<br />\n用DD-WRT好似可以做埋DNS，但係未玩過唔知麻唔麻煩<br />\n有無推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed20bb47caeebf31c4a7decde8b9a02b41899d5","tid":979594,"uid":80455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"自己砌router <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用兩張wifi card 應該做到"},{"pid":"8f5065738ab65b6c7a2287e1f2d27efbad5e736f","tid":979594,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"Google WiFi <br />\nlinksys velop"}]}